              <p class="text-text-secondary pt-1">Evaluate the feasibility of implementing advanced biometric authentication methods within the digital identity ecosystem of Pakistan, identifying potential obstacles and opportunities</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-accent-yellow/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-accent-yellow text-sm font-bold">2</span>
              <p class="text-text-secondary pt-1">Create a bi-modal corpus in the Urdu language for anti-spoofing in remote identity proofing, tailored to meet the specific needs and challenges of Pakistan's digital ecosystem</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-accent-yellow/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-accent-yellow text-sm font-bold">3</span>
              <p class="text-text-secondary pt-1">Develop reliable and robust audio-video presentation attack detection models that can handle anti-forensics and multi-spoofing attacks and perform effectively in diverse and real-world scenarios</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-accent-yellow/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-accent-yellow text-sm font-bold">4</span>
              <p class="text-text-secondary pt-1">Engage with a range of in-country stakeholders to understand the intersection between security, digital literacy, education, and legal regulations within the country</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-accent-yellow/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-accent-yellow text-sm font-bold">5</span>
              <p class="text-text-secondary pt-1">Establish sustainable partnerships, prioritise dissemination and networking with scholars, policymakers and other professionals in related fields via project partners UETT and Stech.ai</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Strategic Alignment -->
        <div class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-6">Strategic Alignment</h2>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <!-- UK Priorities -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/10 to-transparent rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
              <h3 class="font-medium text-lg text-blue-400 mb-3">UK Priorities</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">EPSRC Strategic Theme:</strong> "Building a Secure and Resilient World"</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">EPSRC Research Areas:</strong> Artificial Intelligence, Digitalisation, Data, Cyber Security</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">UKRI ODA Priorities:</strong> Reducing poverty, promoting sustainable development</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Pakistan National Priorities -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500/10 to-transparent rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-green-500">
              <h3 class="font-medium text-lg text-green-400 mb-3">Pakistan National Priorities</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-green-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">National Financial Inclusion Strategy (NFIS):</strong> Expanding digital financial services to 100 million underbanked individuals</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-green-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">State Bank of Pakistan (SBP):</strong> Combating mobile money fraud and identity theft</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-green-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">Digital Transformation:</strong> Building trust in digital banking and fintech services</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- UN SDGs -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-yellow/10 to-transparent rounded-xl p-6 border-l-4 border-accent-yellow">
              <h3 class="font-medium text-lg text-accent-yellow mb-3">UN Sustainable Development Goals</h3>
