                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-cyan-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                  <span>Bimodal anti-spoofing framework exploiting voice-face correlation</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-cyan-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                  <span>Federated learning strategies enabling on-device processing</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-cyan-400 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                  <span>Detection models adapted to local language and environmental conditions</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Real-World Impact -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/10 to-pink-500/10 rounded-xl p-6 border border-purple-500/20">
              <h3 class="font-medium text-lg text-purple-400 mb-4">Real-World Impact</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
